Implementation of FIX 4.2 Constructs
Author:
Lakshmi
  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    AgentVenueListener
    AgentVenueListener exposes the Stubs for Order Executions/Updates/Notifications.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Agent
    Agent implements the FIX Agent Handler.
    AgentOrder
    AgentOrder holds the Details of a FIX 4.2 Agent Order.
    AgentRequest
    AgentRequest implements the Request into a FIX Agent.
    AgentRequestType
    AgentRequestType maintains the Request Types coming into a FIX Agent.
    AgentResponse
    AgentResponse implements the Response out of a FIX Agent.
    AgentResponseExecutionTransactionType
    AgentResponseExecutionTransactionType maintains the Execution Transaction Types coming out of a FIX Agent.
    AgentResponseExecutionType
    AgentResponseExecutionType maintains the Execution Types coming out of a FIX Agent.
    AgentResponseMessageType
    AgentResponseMessageType maintains the Response Types coming out of a FIX Agent.
    DeskHandler
    DeskHandler implements the Dealer Desk's Internal Order Processor.
    OrderPrecedence
    OrderPrecedence holds the Precedence Ordinal of an Order Status.
    OrderStatus
    OrderStatus holds the Status of a FIX 4.2 Order.
